dct_title_s: State of New Jersey Board of Commerce and Navigation - Map of Newark Bay
dct_description_sm: Map covers area from Elizabeth to the Passaic River along Newark Bay. Map depicts the varying water depths of Newark Bay as well as portraying the mean high and low water lines and the bulkhead/pier lines approved by the Secretary of War.
